title: Zeitioactive Man and FallTrend Boy 4/7: Ketanji Brown Jackson, Marjorie Taylor Greene, MLB, Puerto Rico, The Weeknd, 'The Ultimatum'
itunes:title: Zeitioactive Man and FallTrend Boy 4/7: Ketanji Brown Jackson, Marjorie Taylor Greene, MLB, Puerto Rico, The Weeknd, 'The Ultimatum'
description:
In this edition of Zeitioactive Man and FallTrend Boy, Miles and super producer Becca discuss KBJ's confirmation, MTG reporting Jimmy Kimmel for 'threat of violence', opening day of the MLB, the Puerto Rican blackout, The Weeknd demanding the same pay as Kanye, and 'The Ultimatum' getting a season 2!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
